m = magic(5) %create a 5 by 5 matrix

colorbar
In [43]:

colorbar

Generate stream networks with STREAMobj¶

In [57]:
S = STREAMobj(FD, 'minarea',1e6,'unit','mapunits')

S = 

  STREAMobj with properties:

              size: [643 1197]
                ix: [12815x1 double]
               ixc: [12815x1 double]
          cellsize: 30
            refmat: [3x2 double]
            georef: [1x1 struct]
            IXgrid: [12845x1 double]
                 x: [12845x1 double]
                 y: [12845x1 double]
          distance: [12845x1 double]

Plot up the river networks on the hillshaded DEM¶

In [58]:
%plot inline
imageschs(dem)
hold on
plot(S, '-w', 'LineWidth',2)
hold off

Plot the largest drainage basin with its river network¶

In [67]:
%plot inline
S1  = klargestconncomps(S);
D   = drainagebasins(FD,S1);
dem2 = clip(dem,D>0); %dem and D have the same size, clip the portion out of dem where D is not zero
imageschs(dem,dem2)
hold on
plot(S1, '-w', 'LineWidth',2)
